{"tid":2195193,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈原來咁撚賤格 暗地講人壞話唔認帳","createTime":"2020-09-09T04:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T14:24:34.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2972ed55916f0fd7c9d8fd158f15d1ef3bff24c3","tid":2195193,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:20:53.000Z","msg":"現在爭議有立場差異的金希澈和河承鎮<br />\n這位河承鎮是籃球選手出身的藝人<br />\n他在直播中說自己和希澈一起喝酒，希澈給他看了成員照片之類的<br />\n然後希澈在bubble上否認了，但因為bubble內容是付費的不能洩露，所以原貼不能詳細說明否認內容<br />\n接著河承鎮上傳了道歉文後又刪除<br />\n<span class=\"red\">原貼表示河承鎮的道歉文裡沒說自己到底是撒沒撒謊，反正就是道歉，然後又把道歉文刪除了<br />\n總之雙方目前存在立場差異，持觀望態度</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNtLfde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNtLfde.jpg&h=c27acf08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;不久前我和希澈哥一起喝酒了 <br />\n希澈哥和誰在交往大家都知道吧 ..? <br />\n反正在酒桌上<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">(希澈)給我看了娜璉的照片, 還說她和我長得像&ldquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n道歉文:<br />\n關於我最近上傳的視頻<br />\n我抱著抱歉的心上傳了這篇文字<br />\n在上週Twitch直播過程中，我提及了一些人的名字，讓他們感到非常的不舒服和尷尬。 <br />\n直播結束後，我意識到自己犯了很大的錯誤，立即聯繫了當事人，為自己提及實名而造成的不便和尷尬一再道歉。<br />\n之後我在頻道剪輯了視頻又重新上傳的了內容, 又給大家添了麻煩。<br />\n因為是懷著輕鬆的心情上傳的亮點視頻所以沒能檢查內容。<br />\n刪除視頻後 我再次向當事人道歉，對提及了姓名的人造成了難以想像的損害，我感到非常抱歉。<br />\n我今後會注意不會再有輕卒的言行。<br />\n對以上提及的各位和粉絲們, 我都表示歉意, 對不起。"},{"pid":"5d678dcca871ebeb846e0d0202c3749e7d28e083","tid":2195193,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6Ld8BD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6Ld8BD.png&h=f3eead20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 河承鎮近照"},{"pid":"f35e7d32af9afe13a24eb7caa3ff1759341ed054","tid":2195193,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5d678dcca871ebeb846e0d0202c3749e7d28e083","tid":2195193,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6Ld8BD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6Ld8BD.png&h=f3eead20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 河承鎮近照"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"邊忽似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44d65f572f64553a06f463ebff66ea2a8db7267","tid":2195193,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img6.cache.netease.com/sports/2011/9/16/20110916232001821b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg6.cache.netease.com%2Fsports%2F2011%2F9%2F16%2F20110916232001821b0.jpg&h=0b9dddbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4df9f09d6c13bca8e2a2c72866e213e5cd02c517","tid":2195193,"uid":46435,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"藍波能無好人 一定會信希澈老師lor.."},{"pid":"89db0f7629214b79e90f0c6dc024dcefc499760d","tid":2195193,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"好心四十歲傷殘老坑咪搞風搞雨靜靜地拎兩蚊優惠咪算"},{"pid":"251541313dc7dcd0c9ada913909e1bee5c8a8fa9","tid":2195193,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2NTpbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2NTpbs.jpg&h=13a30aa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a407542deaec1c343fac3db8573b08bc5c30be73","tid":2195193,"uid":205928,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"(希澈)給我看了娜璉的照片, 還說她和我長得像&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nmomo係似返個人就分手la屌"},{"pid":"40404166d3704a77d2a9b13dfdfd18f33d9b0ec8","tid":2195193,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":7,"s